					</div>
								
				<div class="slide-image">
					
						
							<img alt="24 May 1999: Patrick Roy #33 of the Colorado Avalanche blocks the puck as Brett Hull #22 of the Dallas Stars tries to score during the Western Conference Finals at the Reunion Arena in Dallas, Texas. The Stars defeated the Avalanche 4-2. Mandatory Credit:" rel="original_file_name:72529268.jpg" src="http://cdn.bleacherreport.net/images_root/slides/photos/000/495/902/72529268_display_image.jpg?1289387623" />						
					
					
					<br>
					
					
					
