					</div>
								
				<div class="slide-image">
					
						
							<img alt="Lenbias_display_image" rel="original_file_name:LenBias.jpg" src="http://cdn.bleacherreport.net/images_root/slides/photos/000/495/170/LenBias_display_image.jpg?1289348571" />						
					
					
