				<div class="slide-description">
					
						
										
					<p>Spurrier lasted all of two seasons with the Redskins in 2002 and 2003, in which he compiled a 12-20 record while losing 10 of his last 12 games.</p><p>As head coach of the Redskins, Spurrier experienced the shortest coaching stint of his career.</p>
