						<h2>50. Jerry Sloan Tabs Bryon Russell to Guard Michael Jordan</h2>
						
					</div>
								
				<div class="slide-image">
					
						
							<img alt="Michael-jordan-bryon-russell_display_image" rel="original_file_name:michael-jordan-bryon-russell.jpg" src="http://cdn.bleacherreport.net/images_root/slides/photos/000/495/877/michael-jordan-bryon-russell_display_image.jpg?1289383779" />						
					
					
